http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/kerala/TN-man-found-dead/article13980118.ece

A 28-year-old migrant worker was found dead in a pond at Kalmassery here on Sunday.Police identified the deceased as Poovarasu, a native of Tamil Nadu. A police team recovered the body after local residents alerted about a pair of footwares of an unidentified person floating in the pool, located at the Hidayath Nagar around 11.30 a.m.Preliminary investigations pointed to the person accidentally falling into the water in the previous night. The person had been staying at Kalamassery with his family for the past three years and went missing about seven days ago.The body was shifted to the Ernakulam General Hospital and a case of unnatural death has been registered.